            <title>[CASSANDRA-6069] Sets not stored by INSERT with IF NOT EXISTS</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-6069</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;An &lt;tt&gt;INSERT&lt;/tt&gt; of a &lt;tt&gt;set&lt;/tt&gt; column type is not stored when using &lt;tt&gt;IF NOT EXISTS&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
